以權謀私，香港的安全瞬時淪陷，警隊及香港的管治漏洞被抖出，威脅直逼警隊內部，矛頭直指警隊高層。"},{"pid":"75a02e018475d024a9318f93d64196f67478117a","tid":1386264,"uid":258416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbd29699c7e36c5fd67b66f820ef8f06a539eff4","tid":1386264,"uid":14983,"like":289,"dislike":0,"score":289,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"689 5000萬查完都話冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadffb9b8c7994f26865b46a2d2ade4cd228c9d5","tid":1386264,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"唔好乜都話無用<br />\n大家乜都唔做就真係無用喇<br />\n<br />\n要勇敢站出黎<br />\n指證警員罪行<br />\n<br />\n有用請幫手推下面個post<br />\n<br />\n【七仔員工召喚】會唔會考慮告警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384819</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ea640930efb3487c7282ec329954effb3d0310f","tid":1386264,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b300a6c5439540eddf4cc3e531a741b5eee9224","tid":1386264,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"真係有機會捉<br />\n林鄭假假地都係習派<br />\n中聯辦江派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"FF下先<br />\n支那要黨指揮槍<br />\n但黑警最近嘅表現畀人有槍指揮港共嘅感覺"},{"pid":"e330a439e08801372be88d2d53b83fca60c310d2","tid":1386264,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:48:55.000Z","msg":"低調d啦，識唔識玩架...."},{"pid":"d2e6442f5cef185426a67d61573e3e75c36a7b5c","tid":1386264,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"最後會由特首放生"},{"pid":"70cf362875106ad9bef8cb63149719d3b8ab07a4","tid":1386264,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"唔計689果單<br />\n<br />\nICAC直接奀打777<br />\n777公開表明唔會出賣黑警<br />\n咁仲有咩期望？<br />\n<br />\n好明顯